59.3	Convention_over_Configuration	Convention over configuration	Many modern frameworks use a convention over configuration approach. A few such frameworks include: Spring, Ruby on Rails, EJB, JSF, Stripes, Kohana PHP, Grails, Grok, Zend Framework, Pylons, CakePHP, symfony, Maven, ASP.NET MVC, ColdFusion on Wheels, Web2py (MVC), Apache Wicket and the OutSystems Agile Platform.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cf/Maven_CoC.svg/200px-Maven_CoC.svg.png
